          startsAt:
            "A concern or allegation at a French-speaking/FWB university such as ULiege, UCLouvain, ULB, UNamur or UMONS.",
          travelsThrough:
            "Local CIS/CEIS/commission/conseil route, institutional procedure, possible ad hoc fact-finding commission and rector or institutional authority.",
