            "UNIC University Research Ethics Committee, European University Cyprus Research Ethics Committee and MedIC policy pages, plus Cyprus National Bioethics Committee when required.",
          endsAt:
            "Institutional REC review, preparation for CNBC submission, or confirmation that national bioethics and other statutory requirements are satisfied."
